      <h1>Dropbox Design Exercise</h1>
      <div class="sub">March 2016 - 3 days</div>
      <p>I applied for a Product Designer position at Dropbox. As part of their recruiting process, I was given a design exercise. I only had one day to do everything, from research to prototyping. I continued working on it for two more days, mainly to build a working prototype. It's a great example of my design process and I want to share it with you.</p>
