          <h3>Design Question</h3>
          <p class="design-question">"Design a standalone tip calculator app for iOS or Android. Use the Dropbox Brand Guidelines to inform your visual design."</p>
          <h3>Requirements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Ability to split bill and tip with multiple people.</li>
            <li>Ability to specify tip amount or percentage (ex. 10%, 15%, 20%).</li>
          </ul>
          <p>On a piece of paper, I quickly highlighted the main concepts and wrote down everything that came to mind.</p>
        </div>

